Changelog for hmcpset.cls
*************************

v0.04
2005/03/10
 - removed vmargin package, replaced with geometry package in template file
 - users should replace old template file with new one

v0.03
2004/09/07
 - bump up to 0.03 for all versioned files

v0.02
2004/09/07
 - made default font palatino, but can change with options
 - added boxed/unboxed options for problem statements

v0.01
2004/09/03
 - created class, based on earlier hw template file
 - problem, solution environments added to 
 - automatic placement of ID block with name, etc. at start of document
 - option to turn off auto placement of block
 - 1in margins by default
